(Episode 4)

31
00:02:45,000 --> 00:02:47,970
I will now explain the scene you'll be performing.

32
00:02:48,270 --> 00:02:49,930
Having killed the real Muroga Jun...

33
00:02:50,030 --> 00:02:51,870
the protagonist takes his place.

34
00:02:52,000 --> 00:02:54,670
His real name is Nakamura Yusaku.

35
00:02:54,800 --> 00:02:57,330
However, one day,
a man who knows the protagonist's past...

36
00:02:57,470 --> 00:03:00,300
a man named Fukuyama, arrives from Tokyo.

37
00:03:00,430 --> 00:03:05,630
This scene is where Fukuyama confronts Muroga
about his crimes.

38
00:03:05,770 --> 00:03:08,430
The acting evaluation will be conducted
in pairs according to your number.

39
00:03:08,530 --> 00:03:09,800
We'll be calling you in order.

40
00:03:09,930 --> 00:03:12,300
Please check your number.

41
00:03:14,970 --> 00:03:16,800
