60
00:04:03,700 --> 00:04:05,870
You're not gentle at all.

61
00:04:06,330 --> 00:04:10,330
You're actually a cunning,
cold, and despicable person.

62
00:04:10,470 --> 00:04:12,970
That's why you killed him and took his place, isn't it?

63
00:04:17,070 --> 00:04:18,500
You too?

64
00:04:20,170 --> 00:04:22,370
Are you also here to get in my way?

65
00:04:23,430 --> 00:04:24,700
If that's the case...

66
00:04:26,470 --> 00:04:28,430
Okay, thank you both.

67
