97
00:06:35,800 --> 00:06:37,330
Hayama-san.

98
00:06:38,370 --> 00:06:42,800
That part in the beginning where you tried to
brush it off with a smile...

99
00:06:43,500 --> 00:06:46,770
really brought out the cunning nature
of Nakamura Yusaku.

100
00:06:47,700 --> 00:06:50,800
I thought that was excellent.

101
